Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:25.90,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.75,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut open my skull
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.76,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look into my head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:31.10,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:32.92,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,know why I’m so harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.59,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could be so brash
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:36.40,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to clash
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:39.58,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,’cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:46.34,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:50.51,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.62,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I try to hear
